{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Paula Lebovics, and I'm 61.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- I was born amidst a very large family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my grandfather was quite well-to-do, and he built himself a big building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the back of the building in the courtyard, he built houses for each one of the children so-- so that there were a lot of children playing in the yard.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had our own little building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, everything is relative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In those days, they were small little houses in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was the youngest one of six children, and my oldest brother was already 13 years old when I was born.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there were lots of children in the yard, and it was always very lively.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were considered sort of well-to-do in a way because of my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the whole family worked for my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother worked for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father worked for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All my uncles worked for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it-- it was by the-- just before the war broke out, which made me like five years old still, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had broken my arm.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my first taste of the war was during that time, just before the war broke out, when I had to set my arm, and I recall it very vividly.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was on a Friday, and they used to bathe the children outside like in a [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What's called a [POLISH] is like a basin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was bathed for Shabbat, and-- and when my mother-- may she rest in peace-- when she touched me, I started screaming when she touched my arm, and nobody knew why.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So naturally, we had to go on to make the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
